  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<h1 class=\"size-38 is-title1-48 is-title-bold is-upper\" style=\"text-align:left;\">獵豹網課可以發問嗎？</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">前兩天S101高一資優數學班群有同學提出一道有趣的題目，授課青易老師、宗翰老師、還有獵豹團隊青昀博士都提出看法，加入討論，也有學員/家長一起參與。<br />\n<br />\n常有家長問我，獵豹的網課是否可以發問，其實，獵豹網課有獨有的「班群」制度，獵豹召集人宗翰老師，所有授課老師，班主任和我都在群內，所有群內的家長和孩子們都可以一起討論數學，形成班群內最好的學習氛圍。而現場課一道問題只能問一位老師，且因為能發問的時間有限制，常常都只能是單一老師單向講解做法，而獵豹班群是大家隨時都能加入討論激盪出更多想法，對孩子的學習帶來真正的幫助！</span><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"edit\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/945878909698128/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/945878909698128/</a></span></div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081406582158830-1ccae4e3.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081406582236391-2b9d51c9.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081406582293755-f6bb9b19.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081406582220670-e090a562.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081406582229642-540dc6b2.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081406582249118-85d2839d.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
